215
00:11:58,746 --> 00:12:01,216
Ibuku sedang sakit.

216
00:12:01,716 --> 00:12:03,887
Ibumu berpura-pura.

217
00:12:03,887 --> 00:12:07,216
Dia akan kehilangan segalanya.
Jadi, dia berpura-pura gila.

